<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-94-0567 </DOCNO><TEXT>The advantage of decentral energy production units, such as small-scalehydroelectric power plants, dual purpose electricity power and heatingplants, and plants with heat/energy coupling for the energy supply toindustry and households are presented. In order to ensure better useof the central large-scale power plants, the author suggests meetingthe short peak loads through the consumer himself. With this, primaryenergy, electricity and costs could be saved. The price comparisons givenrelate to the situation in Switzerland.</TEXT></DOC>